sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant API
  participant Cache
  participant DB

  loop Every 5 minutes
    Client->>API: Refresh dashboard
    alt Cache hit
      API->>Cache: Read cached summary
      Cache-->>API: Cached payload
    else Cache miss
      API->>DB: Query fresh summary
      DB-->>API: Fresh rows
      API->>Cache: Store summary
    end
    opt User expanded details
      API-->>Client: Include drill-down section
    end
    API-->>Client: Return dashboard
  end
